(66, 2, 18, 42, 1, 35, 35, 'Son of God', 'Connection of the Son of God', 'Both passages emphasize the identity of Jesus as the Son of God. Revelation describes Him with divine attributes, while Luke highlights His conception through the Holy Spirit, affirming His divine sonship.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
