(66, 11, 19, 4, 4, 15, 15, 'the temple of God was opened', 'Connection of the Holy Sanctuary', 'This connection highlights the significance of the temple and its sacred contents. Both passages emphasize the holiness of the sanctuary and the reverence required in its presence.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(66, 11, 19, 47, 3, 14, 16, 'the temple of God was opened', 'Connection of the Vail and Revelation', 'This connection highlights the theme of revelation and understanding. In Revelation, the temple is opened, revealing the ark, while in 2 Corinthians, the vail represents a barrier to understanding the old testament until it is removed in Christ.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
