(66, 12, 2, 23, 53, 11, 11, 'travailing in birth', 'Connection of Travail and Suffering', 'This connection highlights the theme of travail in both passages, where ''travailing in birth'' in Revelation reflects the ''travail of his soul'' in Isaiah. Both verses emphasize the pain and struggle associated with bringing forth salvation.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(66, 12, 2, 23, 66, 7, 9, NULL, 'Connection of Travail and Birth', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of travailing in birth, with Revelation depicting a woman in labor and Isaiah describing a woman who brings forth before her pain. This connection highlights the miraculous nature of childbirth and the fulfillment of God''s promises.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
