(66, 12, 3, 66, 17, 12, 12, 'ten horns', 'Connection of the Ten Horns', 'Both passages emphasize the ten horns, which symbolize authority and power. Revelation 12:3 introduces the dragon with ten horns, while Revelation 17:12 clarifies that these horns represent ten kings who will gain power.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
